WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Welcome to CoffeeHub's brewing guide

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Today we'll learn the perfect brewing method

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Start with fresh, high-quality coffee beans

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Grind your beans to the right consistency

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Heat water to the optimal temperature

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Pour slowly in a circular motion

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Let it steep for the perfect amount of time

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:40.000
Enjoy your perfectly brewed coffee!

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Remember, great coffee starts with great technique 